    <span class="govuk-caption-xl gem-c-title__context">
      Press release
    </span>
  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    New Ofsted report highlights need to get matching right
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">Ofsted’s study highlights the importance of getting foster matches right for children’s futures, as well as keeping foster carers in the system. </p>

  </div>
</div>

<div class="govuk-grid-row">
  <div class="metadata-logo-wrapper">
    <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds metadata-column">
